== Getting Started
Note: You should install mongodb database, before using this application.

1. Clone the application:
2. bundle install
3. rails s


== Model
An Artist embeds one instrument. There is an ArtistRepresenter and InstrumentRepresenter. We use 'roar'-rails GEM.

== Reproduce error

1. POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/artists in order to create an artist.
2. GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/artists/:id  => undefined method `representable_attrs' for Artists::Instrument:Class

or GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/artists/:id/instrument undefined method `representable_attrs' for Artists::Instrument:Class
